### Step 1. 좌석 예약
POST http://localhost:8080/api/seats/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": 1,
  "seatIds": [2]
}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### Step 2. 결제 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "matchId": 1,
  "seatId": 2,
  "amount": 50000,
  "paymentMethod": "CARD",
  "idempotencyKey": "{{$uuid}}"
}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### Step 3. 결제 확정 (dev mock — 실제 토스 호출 없음)
POST http://localhost:8080/dev/payments/confirm-mock
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentKey": "toss_paykey_example",
  "tossOrderId": "toss_orderid_example",
  "amount": 50000
}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}

### Step 4. 결제 취소
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cancelReason": "단순 변심"
}

> {%
  client.test("2xx/3xx", function() { client.assert(response.status >= 200 && response.status < 400, "status: " + response.status); });
%}
